title: I Dream of Geno
description:
Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth break down the Seahawks win vs the Broncos last night. Who is to blame for the Broncos’ loss and what are the expectations going forward for the Seahawks? Plus, they give their biggest winners and “woofs” as they look back at Week 1 in the NFL.
